T02TD1281E:133b-1: ba lim tattva sam gra ha /
T02TD1281E:133b-3: gtor ma'i de kho na nyid bsdus pa /
T02TD1281E:133b-4: ye shes ldan pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1281E:133b-5: gnas la sa la bzhugs pa yi //
T02TD1281E:133b-6: byang chub sems dpa' grags chen dang //
T02TD1281E:133b-7: grub thob rnams la phyag 'tshal te //
T02TD1281E:133b-8: gtor ma'i de nyid bshad par bya //
T02TD1281E:133b-9: bskyed rim lha yi dran pa bskyed //
T02TD1281E:133b-10: mdun du nam mkha'i dbus gnas par //
T02TD1281E:133b-13: steng 'og dbus kyi lha yi gdan //
T02TD1281E:133b-14: ji ltar rigs par rim pa gsum //
T02TD1281E:133b-15: kha dog dbye ba so so yi //
T02TD1281E:133b-16: steng 'og phyogs skyong brgyad nyid do //
T02TD1281E:133b-17: spyi bo snying ga mgrin pa ru //
T02TD1281E:133b-18: yi ge gsum ni so sor dgod //
T02TD1281E:133b-20: gzugs med srid pa'i lha sogs nas //
T02TD1281E:133b-21: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i lha rnams ni //
T02TD1281E:133b-22: 'od kyis bsdus nas gcig tu byas //
T02TD1281E:133b-23: de la yi ge nyid du 'gyur //
T02TD1281E:133b-24: yi ge las ni mtshan mar ro //
T02TD1281E:133b-25: de nyid yongs su gyur pa las //
T02TD1281E:133b-26: sku yi rdo rje ngo bo nyid //
T02TD1281E:133b-27: sku mdog dkar zhing g-yas brkyang ba'i //
T02TD1281E:133b-28: g-yas na rdo rje dril bu bsnams //
T02TD1281E:133b-29: lha mo spyan dang bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD1281E:133b-30: sngar gyi thugs ka'i yi ge las //
T02TD1281E:133b-31: sngags kyi ye ge phyung nas ni //
T02TD1281E:133b-32: phyogs skyong bcu dang pha ma rnams //
T02TD1281E:133b-33: bsdus te 'od kyi gong bur ro //
T02TD1281E:133b-34: de las rang gi sa bon nyid //
T02TD1281E:133b-35: mtshan mar yang dag blta ba'o //
T02TD1281E:133b-36: de nyid las ni lha yi gzugs //
T02TD1281E:133b-37: thugs kyi rdo rje sku mdog sngo //
T02TD1281E:133b-38: phyag mtshan sku yi rdo rje mtshungs //
T02TD1281E:133b-39: g-yas brkyang padma'i gdan la ni //
T02TD1281E:133b-40: m'a ma k'i dang lhan cig bzhugs //
T02TD1281E:133b-41: thugs kyi rdo rje rab 'dra ba'o //
T02TD1281E:133b-42: sa stengs mi dang sa 'og klu //
T02TD1281E:133b-43: byol song yi dgas dmyal ba rnams //
T02TD1281E:133b-44: aa las 'od zer byung nas ni //
T02TD1281E:133b-45: gcig tu gyur pas chos 'byung bsam //
T02TD1281E:133b-46: sku mdog dmar po phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1281E:133b-48: gos dkar mo dang gnyis med sbyor //
T02TD1281E:133b-50: de ltar sems can thams cad ni //
T02TD1281E:133b-51: chos 'byung nang du rigs gsum dngos //
T02TD1281E:133b-52: bsams la bdag gi mgrin sogs nas //
T02TD1281E:133b-53: yi ge h'um sogs so so la //
T02TD1281E:133b-54: dza: h'um bam ho: sa lcags kyu la //
T02TD1281E:134a-1: pa'i lha mo bzhi po yis //
T02TD1281E:134a-2: rtag pa la sogs rigs gsum gyi //
T02TD1281E:134a-3: sangs rgyas bkug ste gzugs brnyan la //
T02TD1281E:134a-4: bstims pas chu la chu blugs bzhin //
T02TD1281E:134a-5: tha dad med de gcig tu gyur //
T02TD1281E:134a-6: rang snying sa bon 'od zer las //
T02TD1281E:134a-7: lha mo phyung ste de rnams las //
T02TD1281E:134a-8: spyi bor bum pas dbang bskur bas //
T02TD1281E:134a-9: steng gi lha rnams dkar po la //
T02TD1281E:134a-10: rtag pa yi ni dbu rgyan byas //
T02TD1281E:134a-11: dbus kyi lha la thugs phyag rgya //
T02TD1281E:134a-12: 'og gi lha la gsung phyag rgya //
T02TD1281E:134a-13: de ltar rigs gsum dngos bsams la //
T02TD1281E:134a-14: rang nyid sa bon khyad par las //
T02TD1281E:134a-15: 'od zer las ni lha yi tshogs //
T02TD1281E:134a-16: phyung ste zhabs bsil zhal bsil dbul //
T02TD1281E:134a-17: de 'og mchod pa rnam lngas mchod //
T02TD1281E:134a-18: steng 'og dbus su rang gi rigs //
T02TD1281E:134a-19: de'i rjes gtor ma byin brlabs la //
T02TD1281E:134a-20: ainda'i sngags kyis lha rnams mchod //
T02TD1281E:134a-33: ta la p'a t'a le aashta sappa sv'a h'a /
T02TD1281E:134a-46: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am /
T02TD1281E:134a-47: a'adya nutpanna tv'ata aom a'a: h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1281E:134a-48: blo dman rnams kyis go cha'i phyir //
T02TD1281E:134a-49: gtor ma'i de nyid bsdus pa 'di //
T02TD1281E:134a-50: bdag gis bsal bar byas pa 'dis //
T02TD1281E:134a-51: dge bas yid dger bder gyur cig / slob dpon dharm'a pa kas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
